{"tid":2035302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽]唔應該因為立法會/港島危險就鼓吹取消527","createTime":"2020-05-25T21:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T21:47:17.000Z","uid":203026,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"369664798bad47fc0f7244c73e27a8af789949c9","tid":2035302,"uid":203026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T21:22:32.000Z","msg":"戴定頭盔先<br />\n我同意港島聚人太危險<br />\n唔會再做到612嘅效果<br />\n<br />\n但係！<br />\n當文宣/唔同行動post都已經上曬<br />\n好多人都準備做嘢個陣<br />\n依家因為太危險而取消行動其實會對其他手足黎講更加危險<br />\n係港島打係好大風險冇錯<br />\n但係當日出到黎唔夠幾個人係絕對危險更加多<br />\n<br />\n利申<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係話527應該去立會</span><br />\n應該做嘅係開花/黎明行動黎減低聚人嘅風險同埋分散狗隻<br />\n同時都可以有一定成效<br />\n<br />\n但係今日內一定要有詳細定論<br />\n所以要快啲討論"},{"pid":"e30bac03842bf045393796748efc858c22147b0e","tid":2035302,"uid":203026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T21:23:02.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b66c986469335fe3650f3609d98bdcd9991d8c9e","tid":2035302,"uid":203026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T21:23:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72d2ccc5d017410b07c638e24caf64de1186ea60","tid":2035302,"uid":203026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T21:23:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港獨立</span></span>"},{"pid":"acc2311fc34d3ac289e99e589853ca8d83308da4","tid":2035302,"uid":203026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T21:24:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唯一出路</span></span>"},{"pid":"45586fe95c82128a3bab32c5fd1dfec7557c945c","tid":2035302,"uid":203026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T21:24:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港獨立</span></span>"},{"pid":"032703219d185641e461b0b130413bc429c60719","tid":2035302,"uid":203026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T21:24:53.000Z","msg":"[black]<sp